extendedInfo.description: The original FREE dog whistle app! Just press any of the 4 frequencies on the dog whistle app and watch as your dog is mesmerized.  The dog whistle app is great fun for the whole family and can be used in a variety of settings.Train your dog to do tricks!Train your dog to stop barking!Use it on your own dog OR other dogs!Use it on humans to make them mad!Dog Whistle App Features-Variable frequency tone generator-4 different sound patternsHow does the Dog Whistle App work?Dogs are capable of hearing sounds at much higher frequencies than people. A dog whistle works by emitting a high frequency tone in a range that a dog does not ordinarily encounter. The highest frequency a normal middle aged human can hear is 12,000-14,000 Hz, so donât be alarmed if you canât hear all of the tones yourself. These high frequency tones have the effect of immediately getting a dogâs attention. Dog whistles are typically used as part of a training routine designed to train your dog to do tricks or for behavior modification. A pure tone is much easier for a dog to distinguish compared to verbal commands. Different sound patterns can be used to trigger different responses. For example, two short bursts could mean stop and one long burst could mean lie down. Dog whistles are great training tools and has been used successfully with all breeds.Search Keyword: dog whistle, dog training, stop dog barking, anti bark, dog training app, dog whistle app, how to train a dog with a whistle
